CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782910144
OL,3,CDetention 'only appropriate sentence'
OL,4,Cfor teenage rapists, Court of Appeal
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe hearing, before the Lady Chief
OL,8,FJustice Baroness Carr, Lord Justice
OL,9,FEdis and Ms Justice Norton, is set to
OL,10,Fconclude on Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
